ore":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:47:53.000Z","msg":"而家有幾十蚊車費補貼，連登仔話知你拉晒雨傘，魚旦班人去坐監都無人會理啦<br />\n<br />\n連登仔幾十蚊奶淋病臭晒奶得好開心"},{"pid":"7e5fa9f53a76ad593f70c6374e62ed4e59a6b649","tid":434353,"uid":102132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:53:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"677033869f7a4d6f53dffbec8bdb9d92f037fc1a","tid":434353,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:54:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}